<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0530d3bc-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s1356l"><num value="1356l">§ 1356l.</num><heading> “Coffee” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this section and <ref href="/us/usc/t19/s1356k">section 1356k of this title</ref>, the term “coffee” means coffee as defined in article 3 of the International Coffee Agreement, 1983.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0530d3bd-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/599/s3">Pub. L. 96–599, § 3</ref>, <date date="1980-12-24">Dec. 24, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/3491">94 Stat. 3491</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/98/120/s1/1">Pub. L. 98–120, § 1(1)</ref>, <date date="1983-10-12">Oct. 12, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/809">97 Stat. 809</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id0530d3be-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id0530d3bf-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id0530d3c0-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was enacted as part of the International Coffee Agreement Act of 1980, and not as part of the Tariff Act of 1930 which comprises this chapter.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id0530d3c1-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1983—<ref href="/us/pl/98/120">Pub. L. 98–120</ref> substituted “, 1983” for “1976”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
